正<br />\n咩都食 街邊檔都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e108a872b296e626746e77119c5ed44c71cd7113","tid":27790,"uid":30421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:22:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一定係食野！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我翻鄉下食啲野好撚正<br />\n咩都食 街邊檔都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n越正既野越多...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e8b5cb978048f0e9b0ef8ffa8aeb61cd2a8bc5","tid":27790,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:22:20.000Z","msg":"急屎"},{"pid":"958bc325095ec5f02b4e01f51bf1b490eafa3b1a","tid":27790,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:23:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>急屎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 呢個真係唔講都唔記得<br />\n特登係搭長程巴士搭廁所<br />\n哪兒來的屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a23d446c1f6a6650acce530353c339fa713cccf","tid":27790,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:24:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>急屎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 呢個真係唔講都唔記得<br />\n特<span style=\"color: red;\">別</span>係搭長程巴士<span style=\"color: red;\">搵</span>廁所<br />\n哪兒來的屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3eac1097214fe504525736b41d496f279f56eb82","tid":27790,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:30:52.000Z","msg":"返你老母，你自己返飽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7ff787f2c51b2f199d863ca8c74bc357aba63d","tid":27790,"uid":27445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:34:21.000Z","msg":"岩岩俾公司逼左返大陸做幾日野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49796cb12e7f7f302f7b3e41cf686e8912f3223b","tid":27790,"uid":45077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep